rows.label: bf08450100_0020
rows.name:
To the Holy Grail and her Driver.
We're here to pass on an order from His Holiness.

rows.label: bf08450100_0030
rows.name:
You are to use the Holy Grail's power to
bring down that ship!

rows.label: bf08450100_0050
rows.name: What's wrong? This is your duty.

rows.label: bf08450100_0060
rows.name:
My only duty is to open the way
to the World Tree!

rows.label: bf08450100_0080
rows.name: If so...then we must take the Holy Grail into custody.

rows.label: bf08450100_0100
rows.name:
They just wanted to use Hikari's power
to burn up their little problem...

rows.label: bf08450100_0120
rows.name:
I didn't say we couldn't do it.
But we have to stop Shin.

rows.label: bf08450100_0130
rows.name:
Tell your boss that's what we're doing.
Okay?

rows.label: bf08450100_0140
rows.name: We don't have time to argue!

rows.label: bf08450100_0150
rows.name: If you don't comply, then we'll take her by force.
